Join us for our weekly Tai Chi practice sessions! Open to all skill levels, from complete beginners to experienced practitioners.

Tai Chi is a gentle form of exercise that promotes balance, flexibility, and inner calm. Our experienced instructor guides participants through traditional Yang-style forms in a welcoming, supportive environment.

**What to bring:**

- Comfortable, loose-fitting clothing
- Flat-soled shoes or practice barefoot
- Water bottle

No registration required — just show up! Free for CCAKD members.
